.TH RUNMIRRORS 1 "2026-03-27" "ctxos-core 1.0.0" "CTX OS Manual"
.SH NAME
runmirrors \- push mirrors to downstream servers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B runmirrors
.RI [ \-a " NAME" ]
.RI [ \-k " TYPE" ]
.RI [ \-f ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Pushes repository mirrors to downstream servers using rsync over SSH.
Supports single-hop, multi-hop, and staged push modes.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-a " " \fINAME\fR
Use NAME as the config file suffix.
.TP
.BR \-k " " \fITYPE\fR
Push type: all, stage2, mhop. Default: mhop.
.TP
.BR \-f
Run from within ftpsync.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR ftpsync (1),
.BR runmirrors.conf (5),
.BR runmirrors.mirror (5)
